    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and the <strong>remaining chopped garlic</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the tomatoes have softened</p>",
